descriptionText:
Operation Final Force
Single-player mission

Date: 08/11/2001
Time: 15:30
Weather: Overcast
Wind: Calm (0 m/s)

Allies: USA
Enemies: Russia

A forthcoming bombing raid won't be possible without a clear shot directly to the heart of enemy territory. Unfortunately, The enemy deployed combat air patrols blocking this route. They must be eliminated or our mission will be compromised.

Tasks
- Destroy all fighters designated objective DEE.


Remarks
- A friendly tanker is available for boom refueling operations. Radio frequency is 253.0, TACAN is 22X (callsign TKR2)
- A friendly tanker is available for basket refueling operations. Radio frequency is 254.0, TACAN is 21X (callsign TKR1)
- A friendly AWACS aircraft designated Magic 1 1 is available on frequency 251.0


Flight groups
- Springfield 3(P)    2× F-14B Tomcat    124.0    General    USS John C. Stennis
- Magic 1    1× E-3A Sentry    251.0    General
- Shell 1    1× KC-135MPRS Stratotanker    254.0    General
- Arco 1    1× KC-135 Stratotanker    253.0    General


Airbases
- Sukhumi-Babushara    12-30    258.00/129.00    -    -
- USS John C. Stennis    -    127.5    11    CVN, 74X
